jquery-countdown
================

Countdown plugin for jQuery
```jquery
$('#countdown').countdown({
  debug : true,
  delay : 1000,
  millisecond : false,
  pattern : '{0}-{1}-{2}',
  events: {
    finish: function(){
      if(settings.debug === true)
      {
        console.log('fire finish event');
      }
    },
    progress : function(){
      if(settings.debug === true)
      {
        console.log('fire progress event');
      }
    }
 }
});
```
